{"tid":1440021,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日男肥窮醜毒卻擁超靚女友 狂晒恩愛竟激怒網民？","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:26:15.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5096eadfe996565220e69ab7da0553e14e0420","tid":1440021,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134497/org/271b6bfe1ca04707232eded54df9170d.jpg/nsFUl7LioTGxlIkZEotb-WplnoZ_S4Zsa8spTmvLKU4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134497%2Forg%2F271b6bfe1ca04707232eded54df9170d.jpg%2FnsFUl7LioTGxlIkZEotb-WplnoZ_S4Zsa8spTmvLKU4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d3afa71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134530/org/6c02210bee612a0e5717c63e89385fb9.jpg/kwiOgYzz1AipfZgX7a6LMo0y9egNf6oT_zX_Qf81_0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134530%2Forg%2F6c02210bee612a0e5717c63e89385fb9.jpg%2FkwiOgYzz1AipfZgX7a6LMo0y9egNf6oT_zX_Qf81_0E&h=6a775ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134521/org/4918865871ebc7acb38a96967eb163c9.jpg/Lt3stZfK93XMb8CYSjEvYLtz0HKyF8XqjO2yCYztsgk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134521%2Forg%2F4918865871ebc7acb38a96967eb163c9.jpg%2FLt3stZfK93XMb8CYSjEvYLtz0HKyF8XqjO2yCYztsgk&h=f4f8682d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134529/org/6cc5a3b09f6cf735d900b3bbab2fbe24.jpg/aAXTR2ZE4YuHZszXNmah_1o1bD2df7JnMtK5pzLSuac\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134529%2Forg%2F6cc5a3b09f6cf735d900b3bbab2fbe24.jpg%2FaAXTR2ZE4YuHZszXNmah_1o1bD2df7JnMtK5pzLSuac&h=61ebeac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所謂的「勵志哥」，是泛指一些其貌不揚，但卻擁有女神般女友的男人，是能令所有男生都重燃人生希望的存在。<br />\n<br />\n近期日本出現一名Boss級的勵志哥，在肥窮醜毒的情況下，仍有一位超靚的女友。<br />\n<br />\n日版勵志哥<br />\n<br />\n這位勵志哥叫作ぱるぱる（Paru Paru），今年24歲，是一名人氣平平的Twitcasting直播主。除了肥窮醜毒之外，他還沒有任何正職或兼職工作。<br />\n<br />\n不過，他有一位交往了7個月的超靚女友，而且還經常於Twitter晒恩愛，令一眾網民超級羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n無上進心兼軟飯王？<br />\n<br />\n通常看到這些極端例子時，正常人都會心想：「可能他是富二代或有上進心吧...」<br />\n<br />\n但事實卻並不是如此，在他開始交往後，就於Twitter上不停強調自己沒工作、超窮、廢青等等，還多次要女朋友請客接濟、買衣服給他，因此亦多了不少Haters。"},{"pid":"1626dbd325f86f49edcb5d7af93312edfe97e1cd","tid":1440021,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"個樣幾敦厚"},{"pid":"acf7cc1c7df076a57d0a2865a5cb8de3159a51c6","tid":1440021,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"唔算醜"},{"pid":"e1c7d1c687363d1f8a6af9db32c42ecb2f7c0c2c","tid":1440021,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"唔好攞"},{"pid":"910f5b6141c0e318a09821be42154aa411a90f38","tid":1440021,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"肥姐 唔算醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edbe047d8251216baebcb3650ed03faf8e908ac","tid":1440021,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"910f5b6141c0e318a09821be42154aa411a90f38","tid":1440021,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"肥姐 唔算醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3421e782db7d5a45e37ab5bfa3f0dc3c6e74c339","tid":1440021,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/90911d1dac014362fc